description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Instructional: Perfect Your Posture' from the channel Mac Evans.
The workout falls under Warm-up/Warm-up.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The The Foundation Builder vibe means Strengthen weak points, rebuild, perfect the basics. This is especially good for Those coming back from injury or refining fundamentals. The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Practice sitting tall and prioritizing your posture with Mac while overlooking the Boston skyline.

Max rhythm: 20, Format: Instructional...
